<plot>ALONE IN THE CROWD is the story of a man in New York City who recounts and relives his previous life as an alcoholic. He wanders the wilderness of Central Park as a homeless man following his young daughter whom he hasn't seen for years. The journey he takes, both mentally and physically, finally bring him to an unspoken point of understanding and acceptance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?032523</url></doc>
